OL,3,CBid to decriminalise cannabis in
OL,4,CJersey defeated by single vote
OL,6,FJersey politicians have rejected
OL,7,Fproposals to decriminalise cannabis
OL,8,Ffor personal use by a single vote.
OL,10,FThe debate was called by Deputy Tom
OL,11,FColes of St Helier South who says the
OL,12,Fcurrent rules have created a "two-
OL,13,Ftiered system, given that medicinal
OL,14,Fcannabis can now be legally
OL,15,Fprescribed".
OL,17,FOther countries such as Germany
OL,18,Frecently relaxed their recreational
OL,19,Fcannabis policy.
