OL,3,CBid to decriminalise cannabis in
OL,4,CJersey defeated by single vote
OL,6,FDeputy Coles' proposals would have
OL,7,Fdecriminalised the personal possession
OL,8,Fand recreational use of cannabis "in
OL,9,Fprinciple" and paved the way for
OL,10,FJersey to become the first place in
OL,11,Fthe British Isles to remove criminal
OL,12,Fpenalties for people caught using the
OL,13,FClass B drug.
OL,15,FHe explains: "It was incredibly
OL,16,Fdisappointing to get so close but I am
OL,17,Fglad it shows there has been a
OL,18,Ftransition in the way people are
OL,19,Fthinking about how we deal with
OL,20,Fsubstance users and decriminalisation
OL,21,Fis the way forward.
