OL,3,CBid to decriminalise cannabis in
OL,4,CJersey defeated by single vote
OL,6,F"It was very close this time, I
OL,7,Fimagine if this vote was done 20 years
OL,8,Fago, it would have been in stark
OL,9,Fcontrast to what we saw today."
OL,11,FDecriminalising cannabis for personal
OL,12,Fuse is not the same as legalisation.
OL,14,FIt means that people found with small
OL,15,Famounts for themselves would not be
OL,16,Fcharged by the police. However,
OL,17,Fcannabis would still be illegal and
OL,18,Fplaces would not be allowed to sell it.
